%3EThe%20reporter%20in%20the%20plane%20bathroom.%3Cp%3EMonica%20Humphries%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eb08c674-f9f5-4d3e-b095-7fe2db4ecfbe%5C%22%3EHour%206%3A%20Attempting%20to%20sleep%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20desire%20to%20sleep%20had%20vanished%2C%20so%20I%20spent%20the%20next%20hour%20listening%20to%20a%20podcast%20and%20deleting%20old%20photos%20from%20my%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20I%20needed%20to%20attempt%20to%20sleep%20soon%2C%20so%20I%20headed%20to%20the%20bathroom%20for%20a%20quick%20break%20to%20stretch%20my%20legs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20an%20empty%20area%2C%20did%20a%20few%20calf%20raises%2C%20touched%20my%20toes%2C%20stretched%20my%20hamstrings%2C%20and%20returned%20to%20my%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20this%20point%2C%20most%20of%20the%20passengers%20were%20already%20sleeping.%20I%20strapped%20into%20my%20eye%20mask%20and%20hoped%20sleep%20would%20come%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20I%20was%20restless.%20After%20about%2020%20minutes%2C%20I%20turned%20on%20a%20TV%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e8f0604f-5fa5-4c91-85b4-b0a06c45c1f9%5C%22%3EHour%207%20-%2010%3A%20Begging%20sleep%20to%20come%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20less%20than%20six%20hours%20left%2C%20so%20I%20turned%20off%20my%20TV%20show%2C%20strapped%20back%20into%20the%20eye%20mask%2C%20and%20willed%20myself%20to%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20dozed%20off%20for%20a%20bit%2C%20but%20after%20about%20an%20hour%2C%20the%20pressure%20from%20the%20eye%20mask%20was%20too%20much.%20I%20ripped%20it%20off%2C%20grabbed%20my%20jacket%2C%20and%20used%20that%20as%20a%20pillow%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20continued%20tossing%20and%20turning.%20At%20hour%20nine%2C%20I%20mistakenly%20checked%20the%20flight's%20remaining%20time.%20Four%20hours%20remained%2C%20and%20sleep%20wasn't%20coming.%20I%20was%20antsy%20and%20ready%20to%20be%20off%20the%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20flight%20attendants%20have%20