E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20explaining%20that%20he%20wants%20to%20fight%20back%20against%20something%20he%20calls%20SNARF%20online%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20%26quot%3BStakes%2C%20Novelty%2C%20Anger%2C%20Retention%2C%20Fear.%26quot%3B%20But%20then%20he%20also%20said%20that%20he%20wants%20HuffPost%20to%20use%20%26quot%3BSNARF%20for%20good.'%26quot%3B%20I'm%20looking%20at%20your%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Ehomepage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E.%20Can%20you%20show%20me%20examples%20where%20you're%20using%20SNARF%20for%20good%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhitney%20Snyder%3A%20I%20think%20that%20what%20we%20do%20is%20totally%20consistent%20with%20that%20memo.%20We%20have%20tabloid%20roots.%20We%20want%20to%20be%20journalistically%20responsible%2C%20but%20tabloids%20try%20to%20appeal%20to%20people%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20different%20ways%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20there's%20anything%20wrong%20with%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20what%20Jonah's%20memo%20gets%20to%20is%20that%20doing%20that%20at%20the%20scale%20of%20these%20platforms%20that%20are%20using%20machine%20learning%2C%20along%20with%20an%20endless%20supply%20of%20content%20to%20optimize%20to%20an%20unhealthy%20extent%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20where%20it%20becomes%20a%20problem.%20But%20we%20want%20people%20to%20come%20to%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou've%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20experience%20covering%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20and%20satisfying%20an%20audience%20that%20wanted%20to%20read%20a%20lot%20of%20Trump%20news%20during%20his%20first%20administration.%20What%20is%20surprising%20you%20now%2C%20a%20month%20into%20his%20second%20term%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20were%20planning%20last%20fall%20for%20the%20year%20ahead%2C%20we%20thought%20about%20a%20scenario%20where%20Trump%20wins%20and%20it's%20total%20chaos%20and%2C%20in%20some%20ways%2C%20kind%20of%20a%20replay%20of%20his%20first%20term.%20And%20then%20we%20also%20thought%20there's%20a%20scenario%20where%20he%20wins%2C%20and%20people%20are%20thinking%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%20what%3F%20I%20just%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20this.%20I%20can't%20be%20in%20this%20headspace%20every%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22HuffPost%20Editor-in-Chief%20Whitney%20Snyder%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67bdd1d54e7cbbbe3dc46d22%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224128%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhitney%20Snyder%20has%20been%20with%20HuffPost%20his%20entire%20adult%20life.%3Cp%3EHuffPost%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnecdotally%2C%20I%20hear%20from%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20in%20that%20group.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESame%20here.%20But%20what's%20interesting%20is%20I%20feel%20like%20we've%20already%20gone%20from%20one%20scenario%20to%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20definitely%20did%20see%2C%20after%20the%20election%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20checked%20out.%20We%20did%20see%20a%20drop%3Cstrong%3E-%3C%2Fstrong%3Eoff%20in%20our%20audience.%20We%20felt%20confident%20it%20would%20come%20back.%20But%20it%20came%20back%20more%20quickly%20than%20I%20expected.%20I%20think%20that%20is%20in%20parallel%20with%20what's%20happening%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thing%20is%2C%20I%20still%20think%20there%20are%20people%20that%20are%20in%20that%20other%20place.%20That%20are%20sort%20of%20like%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%20what%3F%20I'm%20not%20ready%20to%20read%20about%20this%20stuff%20every%20day.%26quot%3B%20But%20from%20the%20numbers%20we%20look%20at%2C%20that's%20already%20a%20smaller%20number%20of%20our%20readers%20than%20we%20would%20have%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20surprising%20thing%20the%20Trump%20administration%20did%20is%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpentagon-defense-department-hegseth-media-access-new-york-times-nbc-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Egive%20you%20guys%20office%20space%20at%20the%20Pentagon%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20alongside%20some%20right-wing%2Fconservative%20outlets.%20How%20did%20that%20come%20about%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20love%20to%20have%20been%20in%20the%20room%20when%20that%20list%20was%20drawn%20up%20because%20it%20was%20news%20to%20us%20when%20it%20came%20out.%20We%20have%20credentialed%20Pentagon%20reporters%2C%20and%20we%20cover%20the%20Pentagon%2C%20but%20we%20didn't%20ask%20to%20have%20that%20space.%20We%20had%20no%20plans%20to%20use%20that%20space.%20Our%20assumption%20is%20that%20the%20Pentagon%20leadership%20wanted%20to%20punish%20a%20number%20of%20the%20mainstream%20media%20outlets%20that%20really%20do%20have%20a%20long%20history%20of%20in-depth%20on-the-ground%20everyday%20Pentagon%20coverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDid%20you%20accept%20the%20slot%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20attitude%20is%20that%20if%20they%20want%20us%20there%2C%20we're%20ready%20to%20deliver%20and%20we%20have%20a%20reporter%20who's%20been%20there%20several%20times%20already.%20We're%20gonna%20rotate%20in%20some%20other%20reporters%20as%20well.%20We%20aren't%20planning%20on%20having%20daily%20news%20broadcasts%20from%20the%20Pentagon%2C%20as%20NBC%20might%20have.%20But%20we're%20happy%20to%20be%20there%20if%20that's%20what's%20asked%20of%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGiven%20that%20you%20didn't%20ask%20for%20it%2C%20and%20that%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20full-time%20Pentagon%20correspondent%2C%20did%20you%20consider%20handing%20the%20space%20back%20to%20an%20outlet%20that%20does%20do%20that%20coverage%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20assumption%20is%20that%20if%20we%20did%20that%2C%20then%20they%20would%20jus