Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou'll%20find%20quiet%2C%20tree-lined%20streets%20lined%20with%20charming%20shops%2C%20galleries%2C%20and%20classy%20restaurants.%20At%20the%20circa-1728%20Red%20Fox%20Inn%20%26amp%3B%20Tavern%2C%20you%20can%20eat%20and%20sleep%20where%20former%20presidents%20like%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%20once%20were.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20love%20strolling%20past%20historic%20buildings%20and%20visiting%20spots%20steeped%20in%20American%20Civil%20War%20history%2C%20like%20Mt.%20Defiance%20Historic%20Park.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20it's%20time%20for%20a%20bite%2C%20I%20suggest%20visiting%20King%20Street%20Oyster%20Bar%20for%20fresh%20seafood%20and%20The%20Bistro%20at%20Goodstone%20Inn%20for%20farm-to-table%20dining.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESwap%20Asheville's%20breweries%20and%20outdoor%20adventures%20for%20the%20ones%20you'll%20find%20a%20few%20hours%20north.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228478%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Roanoke%20building%20fronts%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67bdd4664e7cbbbe3dc46d87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERoanoke%20has%20some%20excellent%20shops%20and%20restaurants.%20%3Cp%3EDenisTangneyJr%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-to-do-asheville-north-carolina-best-place-to-travel-in-us-2016-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAsheville%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20gained%20well-deserved%20recognition%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20for%20its%20breweries%2C%20artsy%20vibes%2C%20and%20stunning%20scenery.%20It's%20absolutely%20worth%20visiting.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20you%20want%20the%20same%20Blue%20Ridge%20charm%20with%20more%20breathing%20room%2C%20I'd%20recommend%20heading%20to%20Roanoke%2C%20Virginia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20gem%20has%20a%20thriving%20arts%20district%2C%20an%20emerging%20craft-beer%20sc