EMy%20family%20moved%20from%20Philadelphia%20to%20Puerto%20Rico%20in%202017%20because%20of%20my%20husband's%20job.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWe%20downsized%20our%20belongings%20and%20only%20took%20six%20suitcases%20with%20us.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20weather%20in%20Puerto%20Rico%20is%20great%2C%20and%20everyone%20is%20so%20friendly.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI've%20always%20wanted%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-puerto-rico-new-jersey-coffee-brand-slow-living-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elive%20in%20Puerto%20Rico%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20so%20when%20we%20were%20asked%20to%20relocate%20from%20Philadelphia%20to%20the%20island%20for%20my%20husband's%20job%20in%202017%2C%20I%20didn't%20need%20to%20be%20asked%20twice.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20already%20had%20family%20on%20the%20island%2C%20and%20I%20was%20excited%20to%20stop%20working%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fregistered-nurses-worst-part-being-nurse-jobs-2019-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efull-time%20nursing%20job%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20spend%20more%20time%20with%20my%20almost%203-year-old%20and%205-year-old.%20We%20downsized%20nearly%20all%20our%20belongings%20and%20arrived%20on%20the%20island%20with%20six%20suitcases%2C%20four%20backpacks%2C%20and%20two%20car%20seats.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoctors-explain-why-people-feel-better-near-the-ocean-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ELiving%20near%20the%20beach%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20important%20to%20me%2C%20but%20we%20also%20needed%20to%20be%20within%20a%20reasonable%20distance%20of%20my%20husband's%20job.%20This%20meant%20settling%20over%20an%20hour%20away%20from%20our%20family.%20With%20them%20being%20set%20in%20their%20ways%2C%20they%20weren't%20willing%20to%20make%20the%20trip%20to%20visit%20us.%20Suddenly%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20alone%20with%20the%20kids%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20where%20I%20knew%20no%20one%2C%20wasn't%20yet%20fluent%20in%20the%20language%2C%20and%20didn't%20have%20a%20car%20%E2%80%94%20all%20while%20my%20Spanish-speaking%20husband%20was%20at%20work.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cspan%3EStill%2C%20it%20was%20the%20best%20decision%20ever.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222110248c-4281-448e-9ab1-272d71cdd80d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EEveryone%20is%20warm%20and%20friendly%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20say%20we%20didn't%20face%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-family-to-puerto-rico-for-job-hated-it-left-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Echallenges%20at%20first%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20would%20be%20untrue.%20However%2C%20we%20quickly%20discovered%20that%20Puerto%20Rico's%20culture%20is%20deeply%20family-oriented%2C%20with%20a%20warm%20and%20loving%20community%20that%20embraces%20children.%20You%20are%20always%20greeted%20with%20%26quot%3BBuenos%20dias%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20smile%20wherever%20you%20go.%20Kids%20are%20celebrated%20and%20not%20viewed%20as%20a%20disturbance%20at%20restaurants%20and%20events.%20Coming%20from%20Philadelphia%2C%20where%20people%20can%20be%20cold%20and%20don't%20make%20eye%20contact%2C%20it%20took%20a%20little%20getting%20used%20to%20people%20saying%20hello%20or%20telling%20us%20%26quot%3BBuen%20provecho%26quot%3B%20(enjoy%20your%20food)%20while%20dining%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEight%20months%20after%20moving%20to%20the%20island%2C%20I%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Freproductive-health%2Fpregnancy-symptoms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efound%20out%20I%20was%20pregnant%20again%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Instead%20of%20celebrating%2C%20my%20mind%20was%20racing%2C%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20I%20would%20receive%20care%2C%20where%20I%20would%20give%20birth%2C%20and%20how%20I%20would%20add%20another%20baby%20to%20our%20adventure%20that%20had%20only%20just%20begun.%20My%20worries%20faded%20once%20I%20brought%20him%20home%20and%20witnessed%20the%20kindness%20of%20neighbors%20and%20strangers%20offering%20to%20help.%20Every%20time%20we%20went%20out%2C%20he%20became%20the%20center%20of%20attention%2C%20and%20people%20went%20out%20of%20their%20way%20to%20ensure%20we%20felt%20comfortable%20and%20safe.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20love%20how%20men%20and%20even%20teenage%20boys%20are%20never%20hesitant%20around%20babies%20and%20children%20and%20are%20always%20quick%20to%20smile%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BQu%C3%A9%20lindo%26quot%3B%20(how%20cute).%20I%20also%20never%20felt%20uncomfortable%20breastfeeding%20my%20baby%20in%20public%2C%20which%20made%20my%20breastfeeding%20journey%20easy%20and%20enjoyable.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223279a3f8-aab9-43ba-8329-1c46a670c390%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20have%20helped%20us%20when%20needed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20have%20traveled%20to%20many%20places%2C%20and%20Puerto%20Rico%20has%20the%20friendliest%20people%20I've%20ever%20met.%20We've%20been%20through%20several%20hurricanes%20and%20I'm%20always%20in%20awe%20of%20how%20everyone%20bands%20together%20to%20help%20each%20other%2C%20especially%20to%20ensure%20the%20kids%20are%20fed%20and%20safe.%20I%20have%20seen%20more%20random%20acts%20of%20kindness%20on%20the%20island%20than%20anywhere%20else.%20People%20are%20always%20willing%20to%20help%2C%20whether%20it's%20to%20assist%20in%20crossing%20the%20street%20with%20your%20child%2C%20carrying%20your%20grocery%20bags%2C%20or%20changing%20your%20flat%20tire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20weather%20in%20Puerto%20Rico%20is%20gorgeous%20year-round%2C%20like%20an%20endless%20summer.%20There%20is%20natural%20beauty%20everywhere%20you%20turn%2C%20from%20beaches%20to%20mountains%20and%20rivers.%20We%20spend%20most%20of%20our%20time%20outside%2C%20which%20allows%20us%20to%20stay%20healthy.%20Exposure%20to%20clean%20air%20and%20sunshine%20helps%20us%20not%20get%20sick%20often.%20Having%20access%20to%20nature%20helps%20us%20save%20money%20as%20well.%20Puerto%20Rico%20can%20be%20expensive%2C%20but%20most%20days%2C%20all%20we%20need%20is%20gas%20money%20and%20a%20little%20extra%20cash%20to%20order%20food%20if%20we%20haven't%20packed%20a%20lunch.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe've%20been%20fortunate%20to%20build%20a%20great%20community%20and%20have%20friends%20we%20can%20count%20on%20to%20meet%20up%20to%20play%20or%20get%20dinner.%20We%20get%20to%20experience%20activities%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20the%20island.%20My%20kids%20get%20to%20experience%20their%20culture%20and%20are%20constantly%20immersed%20in%20Spanish.%20My%20children's%20teachers%20are%20some%20of%20the%20most%20loving%20people%20I%20have%20ever%20met%2C%20which%20helps%20them%20feel%20safe%20and%20secure.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20my%20children%20don't%20have%20many%20of%20the%20modern%20conveniences%20that%20kids%20do%20on%20the%20mainland%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20they%20have%20a%20fuller%20life.%20We've%20learned%20to%20slow%20down%20and%20appreciate%20the%20simple%20things%20in%20life%2C%20such%20as%20working%20electricity%2C%20spending%20quality%20time%2C%20and%20watching%20the%20sunset%20at%20the%20beach.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELiving%20in%20Puerto%20Rico%20has%20made%20me%20realize%20how%20much%20more%20enjoyable%20and%20easier%20it%20is%20to%20raise%20children%20on%20the%20island.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-philadelphia-to-puerto-rico-parenting-easier-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740496981000%2C%22visual%