cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20Matter%20What...%26quot%3B%3A%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20Takedown%20Of%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20On%20Kumbh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20criticised%20massively%20over%20her%20%26quot%3BMrityu%20Kumbh%26quot%3B%20statement%2C%20issued%20a%20stinging%20retort%20today%2C%20naming%20her%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20counterpart%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20and%20citing%20his%20%26quot%3Babuses%26quot%3B.%20She%20also%20said%20her%20criticism%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bdistorted%26quot%3B%20and%20converted%20into%20%26quot%3Bcomplete%20lies%26quot%3B.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20what%20abuses%20Yogi%20Saheb%20flings%20at%20me%2C%20I%20will%20not%20get%20blisters.%20I%20respect%20him%20as%20a%20Chief%20Minister%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said%20at%20a%20press%20conference.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I%20would%20say%20the%20families%20that%20are%20affected%2C%20you%20have%20not%20even%20given%20postmortem%20certificates%2C%20or%20death%20certificates.%20We%20have%20conducted%20postmortems%20of%20the%20bodies%20that%20reached%20here.%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20happened%20in%20other%20states.%20And%20if%20you%20have%20announced%20compensation%2C%20you%20should%20give%20them%20the%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20response%20comes%20a%20day%20after%20Yogi%20Adityanath%2C%20while%20addressing%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Assembly%2C%20had%20targetted%20the%20critics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20Kumbh%2C%20%26quot%3BVultures%20got%20dead%20bodies.%20Pigs%20got%20filth...%20whereas%20sensitive%20people%20got%20a%20beautiful%20picture%20of%20relationships%2C%20traders%20got%20business%2C%20devotees%20got%20clean%20arrangements%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said%20amid%20much%20table%20thumping%20by%20MLAs.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnMs%20Banerjee%20today%20took%20a%20360-degree%20view%2