0individual%20has%20been%20permanently%20banned%20from%20all%20cricket%20venues%20in%20Pakistan.%20%26quot%3BThe%20PCB%20has%20taken%20serious%20note%20of%20the%20security%20breach%20that%20occurred%20yesterday%20when%20a%20spectator%20entered%20the%20field%20of%20play.%20Ensuring%20the%20safety%20of%20players%20and%20officials%20remains%20our%20top%20priority.%20As%20a%20responsible%20organisation%2C%20we%20have%20engaged%20with%20local%20security%20agencies%2C%20who%20have%20committed%20to%20increasing%20security%20personnel%20around%20the%20field%20of%20play%20at%20all%20venues%20and%20strengthening%20access%20control%20measures%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PCB%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20individual%20involved%20was%20arrested%20and%20presented%20before%20a%20court%20of%20law%20today%20(Tuesday).%20In%20addition%2C%20he%20has%20been%20permanently%20banned%20from%20entering%20all%20cricket%20venues%20in%20Pakistan.%20To%20prevent%20such%20incidents%20in%20the%20future%2C%20the%20PCB%20is%20working%20closely%20with%20security%20agencies%20and%20venue%20authorities%20to%20review%20and%20reinforce%20security%20protocols%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPitch%20invasions%2C%20though%20not%20uncommon%20in%20cricket%2C%20have%20raised%20concerns%2C%20especially%20with%20Pakistan%20hosting%20its%20first%20ICC%20tournament%20since%20the%201996%20ODI%20World%20Cup.%20The%20PCB%20has%20vowed%20to%20work%20closely%20with%20security%20agencies%20to%20prevent%20similar%20incidents%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20interruption%2C%20New%20Zealand%20continued%20their%20dominant%20performance%2C%20with%20Rachin%20Ravindra%20scoring%20a%20brilliant%20112%20to%20steer%20his%20side%20into%20the%20semi-finals.%20The%20victory%20also%20ended%20Pakistan's%20hopes%20of%20advancing%2C%20marking%20a%20disappointing%20campaign%20for%20the%202017%20Champions%20Trophy%20winners%2C%20who%20suffered%20consecutive%20