20inside%20a%20mountain%20where%20man-made%20caves%20are%20carved%20out.%20Here%2C%20food%20crop%20seeds%20from%20around%20the%20planet%20are%20stored%20and%20their%20genetic%20codes%20preserved%20for%20a%20potential%20apocalypse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20vault%20is%20designed%20to%20withstand%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20disasters%2C%20both%20natural%20and%20man-made%20-%20from%20floods%2C%20blizzards%2C%20and%20volcanoes%20to%20global%20warming%2C%20war%2C%20and%20nuclear%20disasters.%20It%20was%20launched%20in%20the%20year%202008%20and%20has%20served%20as%20the%20planet's%20gene%20bank%20since.%20This%20includes%20the%20genetic%20codes%20of%20thousands%20of%20crops%20and%20plant%20species%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fk0gda29g_svalbard-global-seed-vault-reuters-doomsday-vault-reuters_625x300_25_February_25.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Csmall%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Svalbard%20Global%20Seed%20Vault%2C%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bdoomsday%26quot%3B%20vault%20is%20located%20in%20the%20remote%20Arctic%20region.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETHE%20GRAVE%20SITUATION%20IN%20SUDAN%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20an%20apocalyptic%20event%20has%20fortunately%20not%20occurred%20yet%2C%20the%20world%20has%20seen%20constant%20conflict%20or%20war%20in%20one%20part%20or%20another%20-%20in%20Sudan%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza%20or%20the%20one%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20civil%20war%20in%20Sudan%20has%20not%20been%20as%20prominently%20spoken%20about%2C%20but%20the%20country%20is%20in%20a%20grave%20situation.%20The%20unrest%20had%20broken%20out%20in%20April%202023%2C%20when%20the%20Sudanese%20Army%20and%20the%20country's%20Rapid%20Support%20Forces%20-%20a%20paramilitary%20faction%20clashed%20against%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5C