f%20preservation.%20These%20include%20seeds%20of%20Nordic%20tree%20species%20from%20Sweden%20and%20rice%20from%20Thailand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%2014%2C022%20new%20samples%20have%20been%20deposited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProtected%20by%20permafrost%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bdoomsday%26quot%3B%20vault%20has%20received%20samples%20from%20across%20the%20world%20since%20its%20inception.%20It%20has%20played%20a%20leading%20role%20between%202015%20and%202019%20in%20rebuilding%20seed%20collections%20damaged%20during%20the%20war%20in%20Syria.%20%26quot%3BThe%20seeds%20deposited%20this%20week%20represent%20not%20just%20biodiversity%2C%20but%20also%20the%20knowledge%2C%20culture%20and%20resilience%20of%20the%20communities%20that%20steward%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Executive%20Director%20Stefan%20Schmitz%20of%20the%20Crop%20Trust%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Csmall%3E%3Cem%3E(Inputs%20from%20Reuters)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740493200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fteb7jbng_svalbard-global-seed-vault-norway-arctic-doomsday-seed-vault_625x300_29_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-an-african-nation-is-sending-samples-to-doomsday-vault-in-the-arctic-7793195%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sudan%2C%20a%20country%20bordering%20Egypt%20in%20northeast%20Africa%20has%20decided%20to%20send%20crop%20samples%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bdoomsday%26quot%3B%20vault%20in%20a%20remote%20Norwegian%20island%20in%20the%20Arctic.%20These%20genetic%20samples%20are%20of%20food%20crops%20seeds.%20But%20why%20is%20Sudan%20doing%20this%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-an-african-nation-is-sending-samples-to-doomsday-vault-in-the-arctic-7793195%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Revolt%20expects%20volume%20sales%20to%20jump%2