India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Zinta%20has%20refuted%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EOW%20is%20only%20looking%20into%20the%20case%20of%20the%20missing%20Rs%20122%20crore%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20summons%20to%20the%20six%20auditors%20are%20linked%20to%20the%20scam%20in%20which%20Rs%20122%20crore%20claimed%20to%20be%20kept%20inside%20the%20safes%20at%20the%20offices%20of%20the%20bank's%20branches%20in%20Mumbai's%20Prabhadevi%20and%20Goregaon%20were%20found%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EOW%20said%20the%20cash%20storage%20capacity%20at%20the%20Prabhadevi%20and%20Goregaon%20vaults%20of%20New%20India%20was%20Rs%2020%20crore.%20New%20India%20on%20February%2011%20said%20its%20two%20safes%20had%20Rs%20133%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20found%20only%20Rs%2011.13%20crore%20when%20they%20counted%20the%20cash%2C%20leaving%20the%20rest%20Rs%20122%20crore%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20six%20auditors%20to%20whom%20summons%20have%20been%20sent%20are%20Sanjay%20Rane%20and%20Associates%20and%20his%20partner%20Abhijit%20Deshmukh%2C%20UG%20Devi%20and%20Co%2C%20Gandhi%20and%20Associates%2C%20Shinde%20Nayak%20Associates%2C%20Jain%20Tripathi%20and%20Co%2C%20and%20SI%20Mogul%20and%20Co.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitesh%20Mehta%2C%20the%20general%20manager%20and%20head%20of%20accounts%20of%20New%20India%2C%20has%20been%20named%20as%20the%20key%20accused%20in%20the%20scam.%20Another%20accused%20in%20the%20case%20is%20Dharmesh%20Paun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20came%20to%20light%20after%20the%20bank's%20new%20acting%20CEO%20Devarshi%20Ghosh%20filed%20a%20complaint%20against%20Mr%20Mehta%20and%20others%20in%20Mumbai%20for%20alleged%20misappropriation%20of%20the%20bank's%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20earlier%20this%20month%20superseded%20the%20cooperative%20bank's%20board%20for%20a%20year%20and%20appointed%20the%20administrator%20to%20manage%20its%20affairs.%20A%20day%20prior%20to%20that%