pe%2Fpope-francis-critical-what-happens-when-a-pope-dies%2Famp_articleshow%2F118558997.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fpope-francis-critical-what-happens-when-a-pope-dies%2Famp_articleshow%2F118558997.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Big%20Supreme%20Court%20Relief%20For%20Lakshya%20Sen%20In%20Age%20Fraud%20Allegation%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20issued%20notice%20in%20a%20Special%20Leave%20Petition%20filed%20by%20Indian%20badminton%20player%20Lakshya%20Sen%2C%20challenging%20the%20Karnataka%20High%20Court's%20order%20rejecting%20his%20plea%20to%20quash%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20allegation%20of%20fabricating%20birth%20certificates%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20underage%20badminton%20tournament.%20A%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Sudhanshu%20Dhulia%20and%20K.%20Vinod%20Chandran%20issued%20notice%20and%20stayed%20coercive%20steps%20against%20them.%C2%A0The%20matter%20will%20now%20be%20heard%20on%20April%2016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20rejected%20the%20petitions%20filed%20by%20ace%20badminton%20player%20Lakshya%20Sen%2C%20his%20family%20members%2C%20and%20his%20coach%20U%20Vimal%20Kumar%20in%20connection%20with%20allegations%20of%20fabricating%20birth%20certificates.%20The%20court%20ruled%20that%20there%20was%20prima%20facie%20evidence%20warranting%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20case.%20The%20case%20originated%20from%20a%20private%20complaint%20filed%20by%20MG%20Nagaraj%2C%20who%20alleged%20that%20Lakshya%20Sen's%20parents%20Dhirendra%20and%20Nirmala%20Sen%2C%20along%20with%20his%20brother%20Chirag%20Sen%2C%20coach%20U%20Vimal%20Kumar%2C%20and%20an%20employee%20of%20the%20Karnataka%20Badminton%20Association%2C%20were%20involved%20in%20falsifying%20birth%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20complaint%2C%20the%20accused%20allegedly%20manipulated%20the%20birth%20certificates%20of%20Lakshya%20and%20Chirag%20Sen%2C%20reducing%20their%20age%20by%20approximately%20two%20and%20a%20half%20years.%20The%20alleged%20forgery%20was%20intended%20to%20allow%20them%20to%20participate%20in%20age-restricted%20badminton%20tournaments%20and%20avail%20government%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENagaraj%20supported%20his%20claims%20with%20documents%20obtained%20under%20the%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20Act%20and%20requested%20the%20court%20to%20summon%20original%20records%20from%20the%20Sports%20Authority%20of%20India%20(SAI)%20and%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Youth%20Affairs%20and%20Sports%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Based%20on%20this%20evidence%2C%20the%20court%20directed%20the%20High%20Grounds%20police%20station%20to%20conduct%20an%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20court's%20directive%2C%20the%20police%20registered%20a%20First%20Information%20Report%20(FIR)%20under%20IPC%20Sections%20420%20(cheating)%2C%20468%20(forgery)%2C%20and%20471%20(using%20forged%20documents%20as%20genuine).%20However%2C%20the%20petitioners%20moved%20the%20Karnataka%20High%20Court%20in%202022%2C%20securing%20an%20interim%20order%20that%20stalled%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petitioners%20argued%20that%20the%20complaint%20and%20subsequent%20FIR%20were%20baseless%2C%20motivated%2C%20and%20intended%20to%20harass%20them.%20They%20alleged%20that%20Nagaraj%20was%20acting%20out%20of%20personal%20vendetta%2C%20claiming%20that%20his%20daughter%20had%20applied%20to%20join%20the%20Prakash%20Padukone%20Badminton%20Academy%20in%202020%20but%20was%20not%20selected%20after%20the%20evaluation%20process.%20Vimal%20Kumar%2C%20a%20coach%20at%20the%20academy%2C%20was%20named%20in%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20M%20G%20Uma%2C%20while%20dismissing%20the%20petitions%2C%20observed%20that%20the%20petitioners'%20counsel%20did%20not%20present%20arguments%20despite%20being%20given%20sufficient%20opportunities.%20The%20judge%20also%20refused%20a%20request%20for%20more%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20prima%20facie%20materials%20are%20placed%20on%20record%20that%20constitute%20the%20offenses%2C%20I%20do%20not%20find%20any%20reason%20to%20stall%20the%20investigation%20or%20quash%20the%20criminal%20proceedings%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Uma%20stated.%20The%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20complainant%20had%20provided%20sufficient%20documentary%20evidence%20obtained%20through%20RTI%2C%20reinforcing%20the%20need%20for%20an%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20PTI%20inputs%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740486360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fvib46b8_lakshya-sen_650x400_04_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fbadminton%2Frelief-for-lakshya-sen-supreme-court-stays-coercive-action-over-age-fraud-allegation-case-7792202%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20issued%20notice%20in%20a%20Special%20Leave%20Petition%20filed%20by%20Indian%20badminton%20player%20Lakshya%20Sen%2C%20challenging%20the%20Karnataka%20High%20Court's%20order%20rejecting%20his%20plea%20to%20quash%20an%20investigation%20into%20the%20allegation%20of%20fabricating%20birth%20certificates%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fbadminton%2Frelief-for-lakshya-sen-supreme-court-stays-coercive-action-over-age-fraud-allegation-case-7792202%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BElon%20Not%20Cut%20Out%20For%20Politics%26quot%3B%3A%20Father%20Errol%20Musk%20Explains%20Why%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EErrol%20Musk%2C%20the%20father%20of%20billionaire%20entrepreneur%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20has%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20his%20son's%20potential%20future%20in%20politics.%20In%20a%20candid%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fenglish.alarabiya.net%2FNews%2Fworld%2F2025%2F02%2F24%2Felon-for-president-father-errol-musk-says-son-not-cut-out-for-