20Tim%20Cook%20met%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump.%20What%20is%20interesting%20however%2C%20is%20that%20the%20focus%20will%20not%20be%20on%20manufacturing%20iPhones%2C%20iPads%2C%20and%20Apple%20Macs%20(laptops)%20-%20those%20will%20continue%20to%20happen%20in%20China%2C%20Taiwan%2C%20Vietnam%2C%20and%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EARTIFICIAL%20INTELLIGENCE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%2C%20which%20has%20its%20own%20artificial%20intelligence%20or%20AI%20platform%20-%20Apple%20Intelligence%20-%20will%20be%20the%20primary%20focus%20of%20this%20investment.%20For%20this%20the%20tech%20giant%20plans%20to%20set%20up%20a%20gigantic%20factory%20in%20Texas%2C%20where%20its%20AI%20servers%20will%20be%20manufactured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ERESEARCH%20JOBS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20also%20aims%20to%20create%20more%20than%2020%2C000%20research%20and%20development%20jobs%20across%20the%20US%20within%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESOURCING%20COMPONENTS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Apple%20Intelligence%2C%20the%20%24500%20billion%20investment%20will%20also%20be%20used%20to%20purchase%20components%20and%20parts%20from%20other%20US%20suppliers.%20This%20includes%20firms%20such%20as%20Corning%2C%20which%20manufactures%20glass%20panels%20for%20iPhones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAPPLE%20TV%2B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20massive%20investment%20will%20also%20be%20used%20by%20the%20company%20to%20expand%20its%20Apple%20TV%2B%20service%20headquartered%20in%20the%20US.%20New%20television%20shows%2C%20originals%2C%20and%20movies%20based%20in%20America%20will%20be%20funded%20from%20the%20overall%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESEMICONDUCTOR%20MANUFACTURING%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20has%20big%20plans%20for%20semiconductor%20manufacturing%20-%20for%20which%20it%20majorly%20depends%20on%20Taiwanese%20firm%20Foxconn.%20The%20company%20had%20revealed%20last%20month%20that%20it%20has%20already%20started%20mass%20production%20of%20chips%20of%20its%20own%20unique%20design.%20This%20is%20being%20done%20at%20a%20factory%20owned%20by%20Taiwan%20Semiconductor%20Manufacturing%20Company%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Arizona.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBringing%20the%20Taiwanese%20firm%20to%20Arizona%20and%20helping%20introduce%20legislation%20that%20later%20went%20on%20to%20become%20the%20CHIPS%20Act%20to%20bolster%20US%20semiconductor%20production%20were%20two%20of%20Donald%20Trump's%20biggest%20industrial%20policy%20moves%20during%20his%20first%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20has%20now%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20work%20with%20Foxconn%2C%20formally%20known%20as%20Hon%20Hai%20Precision%20Industry%2C%20to%20build%20a%20massive%20250%2C000-square-foot%20facility%20in%20Houston%2C%20where%20it%20will%20assemble%20servers%20that%20go%20into%20data%20centers%20which%20will%20power%20Apple%20Intelligence%2C%20its%20suite%20of%20AI%20features%20that%20help%20draft%20emails%20and%20perform%20many%20other%20tasks.%20Those%20servers%20are%20currently%20made%20outside%20of%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESKILL%20ACADEMY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESkill%20development%20will%20be%20a%20key%20focus%20area%20for%20the%20US%20tech%20giant%20%2C%20which%20aims%20to%20utilise%20part%20of%20the%20%24500%20billion%20investment%20to%20open%20a%20manufacturing%20academy%20in%20Michigan%2C%20where%20its%20engineers%20and%20academic%20staff%20will%20offer%20free%20courses%20to%20upskill%20workers%20at%20small%20and%20medium%20manufacturing%20facilities.%20Courses%20will%20include%20programs%20such%20as%20project%20management%2C%20skill%20training%2C%20factory%20operations%2C%20and%20manufacturing%20process%20optimisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20HAPPENS%20TO%20iPHONES%20AND%20iPADS%20AMID%20TARIFF%20THREATS%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple's%20devices%2C%20such%20as%20iPhone%2C%20iPad%2C