s.%20But%20you%20can%20only%20find%20them%20in%20regions%20that%20meet%20certain%20criteria%20is%20where%20you%20can%20find%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20prefer%20slopey%20hills%20with%20trees%20like%20the%20magnolia%20and%20of%20course%2C%20bamboo.%20Most%20of%20their%20diet%20consists%20of%20bamboo%20leaves.%20And%20for%20pandas%20to%20choose%20their%20habitats%2C%20a%20nearby%20water%20source%20remains%20key%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-19-at-18.18.21-2_11zon-1740103556-500x577.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Despite%20belonging%20to%20the%20Carnivora%20family%20of%20animals%2C%20red%20pandas%20primarily%20feast%20on%20fruits%20and%20bamboo%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-19-at-18.18.21-2_11zon-1740103556-500x577.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-19-at-18.18.21-2_11zon-1740103556-260x300.jpeg%20260w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-19-at-18.18.21-2_11zon-1740103556-768x886.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-19-at-18.18.21-2_11zon-1740103556-150x173.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-19-at-18.18.21-2_11zon-1740103556.jpeg%201110w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-407791%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22577%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDespite%20belonging%20to%20the%20Carnivora%20family%20of%20animals%2C%20red%20pandas%20primarily%20feast%20on%20fruits%20and%20bamboo%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2